                University Library
              









Libraries





      View Menu
      
Down arrow icon












The UIC Library welcomes everyone. 
The Library has three locations across Illinois, in addition to the UIC School of Law Library.





            Libraries Link Tiles
          Heading link



 
Copy link












                            Richard J. Daley Library
                    

                Collections cover the arts, humanities, sciences, engineering, special collections and university archives.
            












                            Library of the Health Sciences - Chicago
                    

                Includes materials on medicine, nursing, dentistry, pharmacology and other health-related professions.
            












                            Library of the Health Sciences - Peoria
                    

                Collaborating with the Colleges of Medicine and Nursing to meet the information needs of our patrons in Peoria.
            












                            Crawford Library of the Health Sciences - Rockford
                    

                Serving patrons at the Colleges of Medicine, Nursing, Pharmacy, and Medical Biotechnology in Rockford.
            








